Package: RmdImgPaste
Type: Package
Title: Just Use 'cmd + v' to Paste Image to a Rmd File or Blogdown Post
Version: 0.1.0
Author: zhangzhenhao <zngzen28@gmail.com>
Maintainer: zhangzhenhao <zngzen28@gmail.com>
Description: When have binded shortcuts(for example 'cmd + v'), you can just use
    'cmd + v' paste image into a blogdown post or a Rmd file. for linux user, xlip 
    is needed; for windows 7, powershell need updated to 5.1.
